Package de.tum.in.bluetooth.discovery

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BluetoothDeviceDiscovery
    Component Discovering bluetooth device periodically and publishing a RemoteDevice service per found device.
    BluetoothServiceDiscovery
    Component publishing ServiceRecord for all bluetooth services.
    BluetoothThreadManager
    This static class manages the Bluetooth action.
    DeviceDiscoveryAgent
    Agent used to search for bluetooth devices
    Env
    System Property Utility class to determine whether bluetooth application will be used for testing purposes or production purposes
    RemoteNamedDevice
    A class extending RemoteDevice but setting the friendly name.
    ServiceDiscoveryAgent
    Discovery Agent searching services for one specific device.

    Bluetooth discovery mode (inquiry).
